# No em dashes

Never use the em dash character (`—` or `&mdash;`). Use alternative punctuation instead:

- Rewrite with a comma, semicolon, colon, or period
- Use parentheses for parenthetical asides
- Split into two sentences

```
❌ We extended TSDoc — adding custom tags and badges
✅ We extended TSDoc with custom tags and badges

❌ Control every page — not the other way around
✅ Control every page, not the other way around

❌ Method tables, parameter lists — all auto-generated
✅ Method tables, parameter lists, and more. All auto-generated.
```
